###GET(Read all users)
get http://localhost:3000/user-api/users

###GET(Read a user by id)
get http://localhost:3000/user-api/users/vamsi

###POST(Create new user)
post http://localhost:3000/user-api/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name":"prashanth",
    "age":25
}

###PUT(Update a user)
put http://localhost:3000/user-api/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
    
    "name": "vamsi",
    "age": 50,
    "salary": 80000,
    "city": "banglore"
}

###DELETE(Delete user by id)
delete http://localhost:3000/user-api/users/prashanth




