###GET (read all products)
get http://localhost:3500/product-api/products

###GET (read a product by product id)
get http://localhost:3500/product-api/products/100

###GET (read a product by product pname)
get http://localhost:3500/product-api/products/mobile

###POST ( Create a Product )
post http://localhost:3500/product-api/product
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "pid" : 300,
    "pname" : "watch",
    "price" : 1000
}

###PUT (Update product)
put http://localhost:3500/product-api/product
Content-Type: application/json

{
    
    "pname" : "Fan",
    "price" : 2000
}

###DELETE (Delete a product by productId)
delete http://localhost:3500/product-api/products/100

###DELETE (Delete a product by pname)
delete http://localhost:3500/product-api/products/mobile